text: The Lucky Texan is a 1934 American western movie directed by Robert N. Bradbury and starring John Wayne, Barbara Sheldon, Lloyd Whitlock, George Gabby Hayes, Yakima Canutt, Earl Dwine. It was distributed by Monogram Pictures. ==Other websites== * * Category:1934 movies Category:1930s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by Robert N.
